      Please note that your lending score will go down each day this item is overdue.  Your lending score helps others determine how reliable you are to lend things to.
    </p>
    <p>
      To login to the site, just follow this link: <%= @url %>.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for using Lethe and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>